+3. [P3] The shared Glovo-style control chrome is incomplete ‚Äî list mode still uses 36px controls (`w-9 h-9`, `h-9`) at `pages/PublicMenu/MenuView.jsx:156-178`, and neither floating `+` button adds the required white border/ring styling (`pages/PublicMenu/MenuView.jsx:156-160`, `pages/PublicMenu/MenuView.jsx:234-239`). This misses Fix 2‚Äôs ‚Äúsame style in list and tile‚Äù requirement and leaves the list control below the stated 44px spec. FIX: standardize both modes on the same edge control styling: `w-11 h-11` tap targets, matching stepper wrapper sizing, and a white border/ring on the floating `+` button.
 
